---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About Adam Mooz"
	description="Engineering leader, full stack developer, and builder of teams."
	eyebrow="About"
>
	<section class="content-shell py-12 space-y-8">
		<div class="space-y-3 max-w-3xl">
			<p class="m-0 text-ink text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">
				I'm a full stack dev manager who likes building teams as much as I like building software.
			</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-muted">
				My career has taken me through IBM, Shopify, and OpsLevel — each a different scale and context,
				but all grounded in the same belief: great software comes from clear thinking, strong teams,
				and a relentless focus on what actually matters to the people using it.
			</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-muted">
				At Shopify, I worked on platform infrastructure that had to stay standing while millions of
				merchants ran their businesses on top of it. At OpsLevel, I led the engineering org building
				the developer portal product — the kind of internal tooling that makes or breaks engineering
				velocity at scale.
			</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-muted">
				These days I'm thinking hard about developer experience, platform engineering, and the craft
				of engineering leadership. I write about those things here when I have something worth saying.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-2 max-w-3xl pt-4 border-t border-base-200">
			<h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-base-500 tracking-widest">Previously</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-1 list-none p-0">
				<li class="text-sm text-muted">Engineering Manager · <span class="text-ink font-medium">OpsLevel</span></li>
				<li class="text-sm text-muted">Senior Software Engineer · <span class="text-ink font-medium">Shopify</span></li>
				<li class="text-sm text-muted">Software Engineer · <span class="text-ink font-medium">IBM</span></li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-2 max-w-3xl pt-4 border-t border-base-200">
			<h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-base-500 tracking-widest">Find me</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-1 list-none p-0">
				<li><a class="text-sm text-ink font-bold uppercase hover:text-base-500" href="https://linkedin.com/in/adammooz/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-sm text-ink font-bold uppercase hover:text-base-500" href="https://github.com/amooz" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-sm text-ink font-bold uppercase hover:text-base-500" href="https://twitter.com/AdamMooz" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Twitter / X</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-sm text-ink font-bold uppercase hover:text-base-500" href="/contact">Contact form</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
